Package ohos.data.search.schema

Class Schema<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
      • ohos.data.search.schema.Schema<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActionItem, AppItem, CommonItem, ContactItem, DocumentItem, EmailItem, EventItem, MessageItem, MusicItem, NotepadItem, NoticeItem, PhotoItem, PlaceItem, VideoItem

    public abstract class Schema<T>
extends IndexData
    Represents an index schema.

    The index schema supports the following index fields: identifier, title, subtitle, name, alternateName, category, dateCreate, keywords, description, thumbnailUrl, url, potentialAction, reserved1, and reserved2. All other schemas will inherit this class, for example, ContactItem, MessageItem, DocumentItem, EmailItem, and ContactItem.

    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
